<emphasis id="2BCAEAB0FF89F76943340BA2FC8CF9CE" box="[768,796,1516,1541]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="40">tri</emphasis>
(Gr.) = three, 
<emphasis id="2BCAEAB0FF89F76943E70BA2FB8AF9CE" box="[979,1050,1516,1541]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="40">meros</emphasis>
